{"tid":1940940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發]商會會員及其司機往返內地可申請豁免強制家居隔離14天","createTime":"2020-03-24T06:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T07:23:28.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cf998e0e214f615683bfd9c5e751368e323bc4b2","tid":1940940,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"政府疑給商家優待，往返中港豁免隔離<br />\n<br />\n＊　＊　＊<br />\n<br />\n先後有兩名知情人披露，政府向各大商會提供《豁免強制檢疫申請書》，允許往返中港的廠商乃至其司機均享豁免，赴內地返港後毋須強制檢疫隔離 14 日。然而政府從未向外公布詳情。<br />\n<br />\n現時已從世界各地到港的人皆須接受強制檢疫隔離 14 日，從大陸回來的港人亦須家居隔離 14 日，期間不得出門（<a href=\"http://cutt.ly/dtvKoGN）。唯有八項要務獲許豁免。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcutt.ly%2FdtvKoGN%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%E5%94%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%85%AB%E9%A0%85%E8%A6%81%E5%8B%99%E7%8D%B2%E8%A8%B1%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E3%80%82&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1gxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=6913d0e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cutt.ly/dtvKoGN）。唯有八項要務獲許豁免。</a><br />\n<br />\n然而一名在某商會工作的 A 女士披露，商會向成員發出通告，謂「國內疫情正有逐步減退現象」，故「頻繁來往兩地的企業高管或技術人員」可向政府申請豁免，由工業貿易署負責審批（圖 1-2）。<br />\n<br />\n儘管政府公報嘗言，為香港提供「日常生活的物品或服務的人士」方准豁免檢疫（<a href=\"http://cutt.ly/KtvJwGl），但從申請文件可見（圖\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcutt.ly%2FKtvJwGl%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E5%BE%9E%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%AF%E8%A6%8B%EF%BC%88%E5%9C%96&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1gxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=1b6600f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cutt.ly/KtvJwGl），但從申請文件可見（圖</a> 3-4）不止廠商其人，只要填報由司機駕車，連司機也可一併申請豁免。<br />\n<br />\n另一知情者 B 女士披露，有些廠商將申請表給予下屬，要求他們申請豁免，代為返大陸處理業務。據知那些企業皆非生產生活必需品。<br />\n<br />\n筆者兩度致電工業貿易署，兩名職員均答《豁免申請書》屬實，但申請人數太多，正在分流，未能確定何時獲批。<br />\n<br />\n筆者聲稱從事手機殼生產，有沒有資格申請。職員答申請者須要在大陸設廠，並須符合前述「日常生活所需」之要求（圖 5），最後交由主任決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100003868649005/posts/1607643309374608/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100003868649005%2Fposts%2F1607643309374608%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1gxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=01b1a6b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100003868649005/posts/1607643309374608/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"7f594ec1e3bcf3792ba65574fac218a3035f0ffe","tid":1940940,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:14:21.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f614029098315dd2cd5edc00677bd2eea243feea","tid":1940940,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:15:06.000Z","msg":"咁有撚用<br />\n中港司機叫得雞多特別D百毒不侵?"},{"pid":"20e1346a49313531407c3e45d6385164fd665eb9","tid":1940940,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c6b04cb63c9ae01ea40081349d5e28e6abdda9","tid":1940940,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"林奠條仆街 真係死性不改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc61fb7fd21b96d276bf2c5fc3f962b77bff79e","tid":1940940,"uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以有記者問下..."},{"pid":"795961daadd3487577d54d7f52d6343f23fff2ae","tid":1940940,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:55:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c2c92a798907b84eb9fe12ba55031e749462a39","tid":1940940,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:57:49.000Z","msg":"佢地唔係人<br />\n唔會中病毒<br />\n<br />\n定係佢地有解藥？<br />\n<br />\neven 英女皇都要落地牢啦"},{"pid":"a72e2738b92c8a3890b079bbc9463567b387927b","tid":1940940,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:02:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除